article_id:773,category_name:News,title_name:Summon Up to 70 Times For Free! Daily Free Tenfold Summon Incoming for New Players Only!,image_path:,message:<div>A new player exclusive daily free tenfold summon event, which will allow users who start playing Dragalia Lost after <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1570428000"></span> to perform a tenfold summon on an active summon showcase for free once per day, starts <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1570428000"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div>Seven days starting when a player logs in to the game for the first time after <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1570428000"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Applicable Summon Showcase</div><div>Whichever summon showcase is active during the event duration.</div><div>・If there are multiple active summon showcases, a summon showcase will be specified as the applicable summon showcase for the tenfold summon. &quot;One free tenfold!&quot; will display over the tenfold summon button on the summon screen. Additionally, this event will not apply to platinum showcases.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. You can perform a tenfold summon for free on an applicable summon showcase once per day (each day is from 07:00 to 06:59 the next day).</div><div>2. The daily free tenfold summon resets each day at 07:00.</div><div>3. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1570428000,update_time1570428515